org.apache.sshd.client

Interface ClientFactoryManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ChannelListenerManager, ClientAuthenticationManager, FactoryManager, KexFactoryManager, KeyPairProviderHolder, PropertyResolver, SessionListenerManager, SignatureFactoriesManager
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SshClient

    public interface ClientFactoryManager
extends FactoryManager, ClientAuthenticationManager
    The ClientFactoryManager enable the retrieval of additional configuration needed specifically for the client side.
    Author:
    Apache MINA SSHD Project
